Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_MIDCNTCDE(zc) From W3CTR4
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_MIDCNTCDE(zc) From W3CTR4
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_MIDCNTCDE(zc) From W3CTR4
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_MIDCNTCDE(zc) From W3CTR4
Gosub _AFF
